description: Derk and Betty Knowbody struggle to be loving parents by day while at night they regulate the world of the supernatural. From keeping the Hell Hound next door at bay to talking depressing Poltergeists into finding their inner anger, Derk and Betty are the best. But when a high profile case moves their whole family to New Orleans, they will find not only their family, but the very fabric between life and death endangered.
name: GN

description: Former motorcycle dardevil, Vic Boone is hired to clear a woman’s name after she’s blamed for a series of grisly murders. To find the real killer, he’ll have to beat robot thugs, get help from a human fly, and escape the all powerful(not really) Raygun Radicals.
name: None

description: Finnish sniper Tero Toivanen finds out from an intelligence officer that other countries care little for Finland’s plight and they are on their own against the mighty invading army of the Soviet Union. Coping with this disappointment, Tero leads what is considered a suicide mission against a Soviet tank squad seeking to cut into Finland.

Tero gets into a sniper competition with counterpart Soviet sharpshooters. His good friend, Niklas, starts to show signs of being shell shocked and Tero fears that it will lead to indecisiveness and ultimately, death to Niklas and those around him. The world continues to ignore the plight of the Finnish nation against the Soviets and offers no assistance.

Bigfoot and his gang of cryptozoological deviants enter a crime noir world full of mystery, horror, monsters and conspiracy. When Foot's estranged brother Yeti is murdered in the Arctic, Foot reunites his old team of Jersey Devil, Nessy, and Megaldon for one last case that spans back to their very long history together.
name: GN

description: Murder continues with more bots, more babes, more Boone. As bodies continue to pile up, Boone finds himself more involved in the Hunt case than he ever planned. His only hope to stay alive? An old flame, a human fly, and some Pongo juice.
